text: Klenovka () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Klenovskoye Selsoviet, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 341 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 22 km north-west from Bolshaya Sosnova. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Klenovka
